        <enum>(1)</enum>
        <text>in <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Homeland Security Act of 2002/s:2008/ss:a">subsection (a)</cato:entity-ref>, by redesignating <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Homeland Security Act of 2002/s:2008/ss:a/p:10..13">paragraphs (10) through (13)</cato:entity-ref> as <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Homeland Security Act of 2002/s:2008/ss:a/p:11..14" proposed="true">paragraphs (11) through (14)</cato:entity-ref>, respectively, and by inserting after <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Homeland Security Act of 2002/s:2008/ss:a/p:9">paragraph (9)</cato:entity-ref> the following:</text>
<quoted-block id="H393BF95ECEC9422AB72D93FF197EE3D1" style="OLC">
